VIEW_DEFINITION: select `l`.`emp_no` AS `emp_no`,`d`.`dept_no` AS `dept_no`,`l`.`from_date` AS `from_date`,`l`.`to_date` AS `to_date` from (`employees`.`dept_emp` `d` join `employees`.`dept_emp_latest_date` `l` on(((`d`.`emp_no` = `l`.`emp_no`) and (`d`.`from_date` = `l`.`from_date`) and (`l`.`to_date` = `d`.`to_date`))))

select `employees`.`dept_emp`.`emp_no` AS `emp_no`,max(`employees`.`dept_emp`.`from_date`) AS `from_date`,max(`employees`.`dept_emp`.`to_date`) AS `to_date` from `employees`.`dept_emp` group by `employees`.`dept_emp`.`emp_no`
